Detailed Description

Details the location of a firmware volume which was extracted from a file within another firmware volume.

Field Documentation

EFI_PHYSICAL_ADDRESS EFI_HOB_FIRMWARE_VOLUME2::BaseAddress

The physical memory-mapped base address of the firmware volume.

EFI_GUID EFI_HOB_FIRMWARE_VOLUME2::FileName

The name of the firmware file which contained this firmware volume.

EFI_HOB_GENERIC_HEADER EFI_HOB_FIRMWARE_VOLUME2::Header

The length in bytes of the firmware volume.
